		<p>
			His latest exhibition draws ‘Ultimate Paradise’ draws attention to the role of aesthetics in the processes of diffusion and legitimation of authority, 
			which forms social order. Aesthetics in the service of ideology seems to be compelling; its function is to reproduce the imposed behavioral model of preserving social hierarchy. 
			It is blinding and it distracts from critical reflection.
		</p>

